{"tid":1462334,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"人多機場就會自動癱瘓?","createTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:03.000Z","uid":62776,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"92f5728e400c5ab759696856e229bd943fab1e6b","tid":1462334,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:23:36.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n點解?<br />\n即係人多<br />\n就算你唔主動塞住條路<br />\n幫手讓旅客離境<br />\n機場都會自動cancel flight?<br />\n講到尾人數多都係靠塞<br />\n依家只係目標為本咁塞啫<br />\n<br />\n同埋大家都話機場係政府春袋<br />\n咁你都要做野先鍊到人地春袋架<br />\n唔係你d人入晒去<br />\n但個個讓路俾旅客無影響既<br />\n呢d叫幫人奶袋底咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 就算今日係咪主動塞，成唔成功，點都唔割蓆<br />\n<br />\n重點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔做都做左囉<br />\n大家繼續入去坐爆機場佢啦</span></span>"},{"pid":"58dfd33b2f8a18e9d96ada86474873beaaba2c52","tid":1462334,"uid":62776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:26:13.000Z","msg":"政府尋日會cancel晒<br />\n係自己柒"},{"pid":"46404dbf78d07fa02f6aaf2873d9a948e50a2cb5","tid":1462334,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:55:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"485a884feac06fc77c85248696d6b1d9342c6a5e","tid":1462334,"uid":62776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:01:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bdaafa26ef499732dd34ca88d9eb7bfc458e1bf3","tid":1462334,"uid":224731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"係因為塞爆條路, 旅客根本去唔到機場 <br />\n佢唔取消唔得呀"},{"pid":"48cd2d8a85165c7ef64078eae9c07ebb5f07c5e3","tid":1462334,"uid":224731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"－塞爆個機場同交通令政府機管局取消航班<br />\n－走去塞住個入口唔俾人走呀<br />\n前者係機管局問題<br />\n後者係示威者問題<br />\n<br />\n醒下啦大家<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係要塞爆機場，唔係阻人上機<br />\n有分別架<br />\n唔夠人咪和你飛<br />\n夠人先行來行去塞爆佢"},{"pid":"a3f08cb011f7b0baf5e53fe6dadf9ac7b15b2a95","tid":1462334,"uid":294974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n如果覺得講得啱，唔該睇睇同幫推唔該<br />\np牌仔嘅野冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(話我鬼都要講㗎喇)佔機場唔係無撚敵㗎，屌<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/dDbQKT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/dDbQKT</a>"},{"pid":"a4101c158280b8ab0466c3c1298644e0769b5d3e","tid":1462334,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:03:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2BA1MQT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2BA1MQT.png&h=22695365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8a1d95c0d0122907b3dc365a4edab700644060f","tid":1462334,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b0e8b0850341226ab1e8d6c811870686a429f39","tid":1462334,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd2d4010d956d76fcd45017587b993fd1320f447","tid":1462334,"uid":213977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:09:03.000Z","msg":"推"}]}